.home { position: relative; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; min-height: 100vh; align-items: center; }

.home::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; height: 100%; width: 100%; }

.home .content h2 span { font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 800; color: rgb(255, 123, 0); }
.home .content p { font-size: 2.5rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 600; padding: 1rem 0px; }
.home .content p span { font-size: 2.5rem; color: rgb(148, 8, 8); font-weight: 600; padding: 1rem 0px; }

.home .btn { margin-top: 1rem; position: absolute; line-height: 0; padding: 1.6rem 3rem; border-radius: 4em; transition: 0.5s; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(37, 6, 173); box-shadow: rgba(48, 68, 247, 0.6) 0px 5px 18px; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; }

.social-icons a { font-size: 2rem; display: inline-block; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(0, 217, 255); background-color: rgb(9, 1, 27); width: 44px; height: 44px; text-align: center; margin-right: 8px; border-radius: 100%; transition: 0.2s linear; }
.social-icons a:active, .social-icons a:focus, .social-icons a:hover { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(6, 133, 218); }
.about .row { display: flex; flex-flow: wrap; gap: 2rem; padding: 4rem; }
.about .row .image img { margin: 4rem; width: 30rem; height: auto; border-radius: 5%; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 0px 5px 10px; mix-blend-mode: luminosity; transition: 0.3s; cursor: pointer; }
.about .row .content p { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: Nunito; font-weight: 600; text-transform: none; }
.about .row .content .box-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; font-family: Nunito; font-weight: 600; }

.resumebtn .btn { padding: 1.7rem 3rem; border-radius: 0.5em; transition: 0.3s; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(37, 6, 173); box-shadow: rgba(48, 68, 247, 0.6) 0px 5px 10px; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; }
.skills .container { background: rgba(0, 0, 22, 0.4); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; width: 90%; margin: 2rem auto auto; }
.skills .container .row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.8rem; }
.skills .container .bar { margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 4px 10px; background: rgba(0, 0, 22, 0.9); transition: 0.2s; }
.skills .container .bar .info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
.skills .container .bar .info span { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 500; font-family: Poppins; margin-left: 0.5rem; }
.education .qoute { font-size: 1.5rem; text-align: center; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

.education .box-container .box img { object-fit: cover; position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; }

.education .box-container .box .content h3 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: rgb(1, 41, 112); padding: 0.5rem 0px; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; margin-left: 1rem; }
.education h4 { font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(34, 109, 0); text-align: left; margin: 1rem; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; }
.work .box-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem; }

.work .box-container .box .content { height: 100%; width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 85%; left: 0px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

.work .box-container .box .content .tag { display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; height: 4.5rem; width: 100%; padding-left: 1rem; background: rgb(255, 217, 0); }
.work .desc { margin: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
.work .desc .btns { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; width: 100%; margin-top: 2rem; }

.work .desc .btns .btn { line-height: 0; display: inline; padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin-right: 2rem; }

.work .viewall .btn { position: relative; line-height: 0; padding: 1.6rem 3rem; border-radius: 0.5em; transition: 0.5s; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 700; border: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgba(65, 84, 241, 0.4) 0px 5px 10px; text-align: center; }
.work .viewall .btn span { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.7rem; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; }

.experience .container { padding: 10px 40px; position: relative; background-color: inherit; width: 50%; }

.experience .container::after { content: ""; position: absolute; width: 25px; height: 25px; right: -17px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 4px solid rgb(255, 159, 85); top: 15px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 100; font-size: 1.89rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(2, 9, 75); font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free"; }

.experience .left::before { content: " "; height: 0px; position: absolute; top: 22px; width: 0px; z-index: 1; right: 30px; border-style: solid; border-image: initial; border-width: 10px 0px 10px 10px; border-color: transparent transparent transparent rgb(246, 140, 9); }

.experience .right::before { content: " "; height: 0px; position: absolute; top: 22px; width: 0px; z-index: 1; left: 30px; border-style: solid; border-image: initial; border-width: 10px 10px 10px 0px; border-color: transparent rgb(246, 140, 9) transparent transparent; }

.morebtn .btn span { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.7rem; font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; }

.contact .container .content { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }

About Me

About Me

I'm Ayush

Student

I am a highly motivated high school graduate with a dynamic array of interests spanning Computer Science, Social Entrepreneurship, and Education. These passions have been cultivated through a combination of academic exploration, personal experiences, and a genuine curiosity about the world around me.


In the realm of Computer Science, I have not only excelled in coursework but have actively sought out opportunities to apply my skills. I've engaged in collaborative coding projects and delved into various programming languages and innovative technologies. My proficiency extends beyond the classroom, as I have conducted research and published a paper on Human-Computer Interaction and AI Ethics. I've also presented my findings to audiences of over 400 people on topics such as Convolutional Neural Networks, Long-Short Term Memory Networks, and Gated Recurrent Units. Currently, I am immersed in Large Language Model Research, aiming to contribute to the field and publish my work soon.


On the social entrepreneurship front, my journey has been shaped by a desire to impact communities positively. Drawing inspiration from real-world issues, I have initiated and participated in projects that address societal challenges. Whether organizing fundraisers for Edukul or collaborating with like-minded individuals on community-driven initiatives such as School Simplified or GreenBhumi, I am committed to leveraging entrepreneurial principles for the betterment of society.


In the field of education, my dedication as a student goes beyond academic pursuits; it is deeply rooted in a personal connection to the transformative power of education. Visiting my village annually, I witnessed children who were unable to access schools and were compelled to work as laborers in shops. This stark reality illuminated the profound lack of educational opportunities. It was a poignant realization that something my mother had always emphasized and sacrificed for was a privilege out of reach for many in my community. This realization led to the founding of Edukul in my freshman year, aiming to provide children across different Indian states with resources such as weekly teaching sessions, stationery drives, and more.


Fueling my pursuits is a global outlook that stems from a genuine appreciation for cultural diversity and a curiosity about different perspectives. This worldview is not only reflected in my academic choices but also in my eagerness to embrace diverse learning experiences, such as participating in international summer programs, engaging in cross-cultural collaborations, or volunteering in global initiatives.


Looking ahead, I am excited about channeling my multifaceted passions into meaningful innovation and social impact during my future studies and career. I am particularly drawn to projects and initiatives integrating technology, entrepreneurship, and education to address pressing societal challenges.


Away from the academic and professional spheres, I find solace and inspiration in the world of visual arts. During my free time, you'll likely find me immersed in the creative process, painting, and expressing myself visually. This artistic outlet serves as a form of relaxation and contributes to my holistic approach to personal and professional development.


Feel free to explore my Visual Arts Resume below if that's something that interests you :D
